    "body": "HeartMonitor is a thing of the controller. You need to set the values in the Engine config:\n\n```\nc.EngineFactory.hb_check_period = 2000 # time in ms\nc.EngineFactory.hb_max_misses = 3\n```\n\nJust generate a new config and you see the new config values (commented out).\n\nAnyway: if you have this applied, stopping the controller should result in a stopped engine after some seconds. Can you please check that the version you are using is really patched and generates the new config settings? Starting the engine with log_level set to debug will also result in warnings when there are no pings from the controller anymore.\n"
  },
