    "body": "I installed IPython from your engine_hb_monitor branch. Last commit on 'git log' is 1719e9d and /Library/Python/2.7/site-packages/IPython/utils/_sysinfo.py has\n\n```\n# GENERATED BY setup.py\ncommit = \"1719e9d\"\n```\n\nSo I should have the correct version installed.\n\nOn my system, IPYTHONDIR is set to \"/usr/local/drqueue/ipython\".\n\nI deleted ipengine_config.py in $IPYTHONDIR/profile_default/ and created a new config:\n\n```\n$ ipengine --init --debug\n2012-10-06 23:12:24,180.180 [IPEngineApp] Config changed:\n2012-10-06 23:12:24,180.180 [IPEngineApp] {'IPEngineApp': {'copy_config_files': True, 'log_level': 10, 'auto_create': True}}\n2012-10-06 23:12:24,181.181 [IPEngineApp] Using existing profile dir: u'/usr/local/drqueue/ipython/profile_default'\n2012-10-06 23:12:24,195.195 [IPEngineApp] Generating default config file: u'/usr/local/drqueue/ipython/profile_default/ipengine_config.py'\n2012-10-06 23:12:24,195.195 [IPEngineApp] Searching path [u'/usr/local/drqueue/ipython/profile_default', u'/usr/local/drqueue/ipython/profile_default'] for config files\n2012-10-06 23:12:24,196.196 [IPEngineApp] Attempting to load config file: ipython_config.py\n2012-10-06 23:12:24,196.196 [IPEngineApp] Config file ipython_config.py not found\n2012-10-06 23:12:24,196.196 [IPEngineApp] Attempting to load config file: ipengine_config.py\n2012-10-06 23:12:24,197.197 [IPEngineApp] Loaded config file: /usr/local/drqueue/ipython/profile_default/ipengine_config.py\n2012-10-06 23:12:24.198 [IPEngineApp] url_file u'/usr/local/drqueue/ipython/profile_default/security/ipcontroller-engine.json' not found\n2012-10-06 23:12:24.198 [IPEngineApp] Waiting up to 5.0 seconds for it to arrive.\n2012-10-06 23:12:29.256 [IPEngineApp] Fatal: url file never arrived: /usr/local/drqueue/ipython/profile_default/security/ipcontroller-engine.json\n2012-10-06 23:12:29.256 [IPEngineApp] Exiting application: ipengine\n```\n\nNow, the default values for \"c.EngineFactory.hb_check_period\" and \"c.EngineFactory.hb_max_misses\" appear in the config:\n\n```\n$ cd /usr/local/drqueue/ipython/profile_default\n$ grep hb ipengine_config.py \n# c.EngineFactory.hb_max_misses = 5\n# c.EngineFactory.hb_check_period = 5000\n$\n```\n\nThe engine stops when I stop the controller:\n\n```\n$ ipengine --debug\n2012-10-06 23:14:51,739.739 [IPEngineApp] Config changed:\n2012-10-06 23:14:51,739.739 [IPEngineApp] {'IPEngineApp': {'log_level': 10}}\n2012-10-06 23:14:51,741.741 [IPEngineApp] Using existing profile dir: u'/usr/local/drqueue/ipython/profile_default'\n2012-10-06 23:14:51,741.741 [IPEngineApp] Searching path [u'/usr/local/drqueue/ipython/profile_default', u'/usr/local/drqueue/ipython/profile_default'] for config files\n2012-10-06 23:14:51,741.741 [IPEngineApp] Attempting to load config file: ipython_config.py\n2012-10-06 23:14:51,742.742 [IPEngineApp] Config file ipython_config.py not found\n2012-10-06 23:14:51,742.742 [IPEngineApp] Attempting to load config file: ipengine_config.py\n2012-10-06 23:14:51,743.743 [IPEngineApp] Loaded config file: /usr/local/drqueue/ipython/profile_default/ipengine_config.py\n2012-10-06 23:14:51.744 [IPEngineApp] Loading url_file u'/usr/local/drqueue/ipython/profile_default/security/ipcontroller-engine.json'\n2012-10-06 23:14:51.744 [IPEngineApp] Config changed:\n2012-10-06 23:14:51.744 [IPEngineApp] {'RegistrationFactory': {}, 'EngineFactory': {'url': u'tcp://192.168.1.51:10101', 'location': u'192.168.1.51', 'sshserver': u''}, 'Session': {'packer': u'json', 'unpacker': u'json', 'key': '4318a387-e68a-4309-8e11-d77d2911fbc2'}, 'IPEngineApp': {'log_level': 10}, 'ProfileDir': {}}\n2012-10-06 23:14:51.772 [IPEngineApp] Registering with controller at tcp://192.168.1.51:10101\n2012-10-06 23:14:51.990 [IPEngineApp] Using existing profile dir: u'/usr/local/drqueue/ipython/profile_default'\n2012-10-06 23:14:51.991 [IPEngineApp] Completed registration with id 0\n2012-10-06 23:14:54.008 [IPEngineApp] Received a ping: ['', '9.00100398064']\n2012-10-06 23:14:57.009 [IPEngineApp] Received a ping: ['', '12.0011351109']\n2012-10-06 23:15:00.007 [IPEngineApp] Received a ping: ['', '15.0005130768']\n2012-10-06 23:15:06.773 [IPEngineApp] No heartbeat in the last 5000 ms (1 time(s) in a row).\n2012-10-06 23:15:11.774 [IPEngineApp] No heartbeat in the last 5000 ms (2 time(s) in a row).\n2012-10-06 23:15:16.773 [IPEngineApp] No heartbeat in the last 5000 ms (3 time(s) in a row).\n2012-10-06 23:15:21.773 [IPEngineApp] No heartbeat in the last 5000 ms (4 time(s) in a row).\n2012-10-06 23:15:26.774 [IPEngineApp] No heartbeat in the last 5000 ms (5 time(s) in a row).\n2012-10-06 23:15:26.774 [IPEngineApp] Maximum number of heartbeats misses reached (5 times 5000 ms), shutting down.\n$\n```\n\nIt seems to work. Thanks a lot!\n\nThis feature is really important to me, because I need to restart the controller from time to time while several engines are connected. Each engine runs in a wrapper script which restarts the engine process automatically. So all engines should be back soon, once the controller is available again.\n"
